snippet.title: Studson Studio
snippet.description: Hey, I'm Studson! I'm a crafter and model maker that likes building miniatures, models, and dioramas inspired by video games tv, and movies that I like. You'll find videos here walking through my creative process so you can build these things too, if you actually wanted to for some wild reason.
